label chapt_1_part_1_cin:
  show cin neutral at center
  with dissolve

  cin "For me... Being hyperpregnant is nice, but..."

  cin "I just couldn't find the father of my babies because I couldn't remember who he looked like before I got drunk..."

  cin "Although my parents tried to reassure me that they will commit themselves to help me out..."

  "Cindy then put her hand on her belly."

  cin "I'm just worried that not all of them get the care they want..."

  show cin babykicks at center
  with dissolve

  "Sure enough, some of them began kicking upon feeling her hand."

  cin "But now I know that I'm not alone, and I thank Dijonay and the others..."

  hide cin babykicks with dissolve

  jump chapt_1_part_1_choices
